  "texts": [
    "These entities may include personal names, organizational names, geographic locations, dates, and other categories.",
    "CoNLL2003 (Tjong Kim Sang and De Meulder, 2003) is a classic benchmark dataset in the field of NER.",
    "It categorizes entity types into 4 classes.",
    "OntoNotes 5.0 (Weischedel et al, 2012) expands into an NER task dataset based on the corpus and provides 18 entity types.",
    "Subsequently, WUNT2017 (Derczynski et al, 2017) focuses on models' ability to recognize emerging named entities in new contexts within the NER task."
